Original Dataset: UrbanSound8K

Description:
The UrbanSound8K dataset contains 8732 labeled audio clips (<=4 seconds) from 10 urban sound classes such as sirens, car horns, dog barks, drilling, and street music. :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}

Dataset Classes:
- Air Conditioner
- Car Horn
- Children Playing
- Dog Bark
- Drilling
- Engine Idling
- Gun Shot
- Jackhammer
- Siren
- Street Music
